name: Tangbohu buff effector 唐伯虎效果增益巴福
description:
Tangbohu buff effector

It is a very interesting little toy that can enhance the details of the screen and provide more fun

Different weights will cause different things to happen

A weight of 0 is definitely not recommended, as it will damage the image and turn it into something strange

The image with a weight between 0.1 and 1 will attempt to be split into multiple parts, with multiple characters appearing, and may also exist as various small characters such as picture frames

Weight>1<2, the image returns to a whole block and adds more details, resulting in higher saturation

When the weight>2, the screen starts to lose control, and the character's face may show some unnecessary details

Anyway, it's just fun,

Tangbohu buff effector

是一个非常有意思的小玩具，他能够增强画面的细节，提供更多的乐趣

不同的权重会发生不同的事情

权重为0绝对不推荐，会破坏画面变成奇奇怪怪的东西

权重0.1-1之间画面会尝试分割成多份出现多个人物，也有可能以画框等各种小人存在

权重>1 <2画面回归一整块并且添加了更多的细节，饱和度也更高

权重>2 画面开始失控人物脸部会出现一些不需要的细节

总之就是很好玩，可以试一下
